How to containerise spring boot app
1) use dockerfile
2) use spring boot maven plugin: run below command
 ./mvnw spring-boot:build-image "-Dspring-boot.build-image.imageName=jobbackend"
 so it will create a docker image named jobbackend and we can push using:
 docker tag jobbackend:latest harshaakoliya20102003/firstjobimage:latest  => tag local image to docker registry name
 docker push harshaakoliya20102003/firstjobimage:latest

